title: Palindrome Partitioning III
content:
You are given a string  containing lowercase letters and an integer . You need to :

First, change some characters of  to other lowercase English letters.
Then divide  into  non-empty disjoint substrings such that each substring is palindrome.

Return the minimal number of characters that you need to change to divide the string.
 






 


.
 only contains lowercase English letters.
